467
00:26:05,459 --> 00:26:07,399
I thought long and hard all night.

468
00:26:08,330 --> 00:26:11,070
All the weird things you've done so far.

469
00:26:11,740 --> 00:26:14,010
When you told me that you liked Se Gyeong,

470
