513
00:28:01,010 --> 00:28:04,080
(20 Years of Excellence, Traditional Chinese Cuisine)

514
00:28:06,050 --> 00:28:08,149
As you know, we don't have much time left until the festival.

515
00:28:09,490 --> 00:28:11,819
But they say, after a rainy day, the soil... Anyway,

516
00:28:11,820 --> 00:28:12,959
we can pull this off.

517
00:28:13,389 --> 00:28:14,859
- Let's go. - With that said,

518
00:28:15,060 --> 00:28:16,129
